-\cos(x)u_x
u\in C^2(\Omega), \Omega\subset\mathbb{R}^2
-\cos(x)u_x
 \xi:=-x-\cos(x)+y, \eta:=x-\cos(x)+y 
 x = \frac 12(\eta - \xi) 
 -u_x\cos x = -\Biggl(\left(\sin\frac {\eta-\xi}2 - 1\right)u_\xi + \left(1+\sin\frac {\eta -\xi}2\right)u_\eta\Biggr)\cos \frac{\eta-\xi}2 
u_{xx}
\def\x{\frac{\eta-\xi}2}
